# evaluate()

**Instance Method**

Causes the receiver to evaluate its position.

## Declaration

```swift
func evaluate()
```

## Discussion

Calling [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSPositionalSpecifier/insertionContainer], [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSPositionalSpecifier/insertionKey], [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSPositionalSpecifier/insertionIndex], or [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSPositionalSpecifier/insertionReplaces] also causes the receiver to be evaluated, if it hasn’t already been evaluated.
